      "prompt": "Fetch current weather for Guangzhou using simple wttr.in text format:\n```bash\ncurl -s \"https://wttr.in/Guangzhou?format=%C+%t+%h+%w\"\n```\nThis returns: \"Rain Shower +29\u00b0C 84% 21km/h\" (condition, temp, humidity, wind).\nIf that fails (exit code != 0 or empty output), fallback to weather.com.cn HTTP API:\n```bash\ncurl -sL -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0\" -H \"Referer: http://www.weather.com.cn/\" \"http://d1.weather.com.cn/sk_2d/101280101.html\"\n```\nParse the JSON from `var dataSK={...}` and output: \"\u5e7f\u5dde: [weather] [temp]\u00b0C [humidity] [wind]\".\nDeliver the result via Telegram.",
